Class PostgresFactory

java.lang.Object
fr.polytech.picknpic.persist.AbstractFactory
fr.polytech.picknpic.persist.postgres.PostgresFactory
public class PostgresFactory extends AbstractFactory
A factory class for creating PostgreSQL-specific DAO implementations. Extends the AbstractFactory and provides PostgreSQL-specific DAOs.
